cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

This paper is about building goal-oriented dialogue systems, which involves natural language understanding, policy learning, and transfer learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and understanding. The paper also uses machine learning techniques such as deep reinforcement learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the success rate and efficiency of the dialogue system, which could fall under cs.SD (Software Engineering) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
